('19df4d89-0ad3-4d4c-9587-b58e85fcb30b', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '13½\" WO34HC-4 / Honeycomb', 0, 0, '53beb2e3-0228-4ed6-b695-ca10d76e3cbb', '2026-03-18 00:41:02.744', '2026-04-02 06:57:16.543', '<ul><li><p>Rigid honeycomb cone (black fiberglass skin layers)</p></li><li><p>Large vented motor system with undercut pole piece and dual shorting rings</p></li><li><p>Vented cast aluminum chassis</p></li><li><p>Linear symmetric suspension</p></li><li><p>Soft low damping rubber surround</p></li><li><p>3″ copper voice coil with non-conductive fiberglass former</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li></ul>', 'wo34hc-4', 'admin', 1, '', 0, '', '', '', 0, '/uploads/productimage/13.5 inch SATORI WO34HC-4.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/13.5-inch-SATORI-WO34HC-4-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/13.5-inch-SATORI-WO34HC-4-frequency-response.jpg', ''),
('1b5a2c2c-1e00-4e88-81d9-490a8c3ded10', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', 'TW29D-B / Fabric', 0, 0, '28c45742-6d1f-44bd-915b-f940e30caf92', '2024-05-08 03:44:12.242', '2026-05-28 06:57:11.244', '<ul><li><p>Large surround dome for increased acoustic output</p></li><li><p>Dual balanced compression chamber for improved dynamics</p></li><li><p>Dual copper caps for absolute minimum voice coil inductance and minimum phase shift</p></li><li><p>Two part aluminium faceplate with integrated mechanical decoupling</p></li><li><p>Saturation controlled motor system with T-shaped pole piece for lower distortion</p></li><li><p>Non-reflective cast aluminium chamber with optimized damping for improved dynamics</p></li><li><p>Flow optimized vented pole piece for optimum coupling to rear chamber</p></li><li><p>CCAW voice coil for low moving mass</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li><li><p>Low resonance frequency for extended range</p></li></ul>', 'tw29d-b', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/SATORI TW29D-B.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/SATORI TW29D-B-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/SATORI TW29D-B-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('1c75ecd3-003e-4c86-a8c3-6a3788abea4c', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', 'Ara Be', 0, 0, '28c45742-6d1f-44bd-915b-f940e30caf92', '2024-05-08 02:18:40.279', '2026-04-30 01:57:01.537', '<p>The ARA Be is a 2-way stand mount kit which takes the ARA performance to the highest level with the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://webdemosbe.xyz/products/tw29bn\">SATORI TW29BN</a> Beryllium tweeter and revised crossover. The TW29BN has been independently announced by many as the best tweeter in the world.</p><p>ARA is the highest point of komodo Island in Indonesia and particularly notable as the habitat of the spectacular and mythical Komodo dragons. The ARA kit is designed to deliver top level transparent and dynamic sound reproduction</p><p>The ARA’s faceted baffle is specially designed to reduce high frequency diffraction and yields superb imaging qualities. A further 7° reclined cabinet ensures time alignment resulting in sublime staging and pin point placement of instruments.</p><p>The cabinet is masterfully crafted from 18 mm MDF with internal bracing to distribute cabinet vibrations and lower sound coloration. Unwanted reflection are minimized by wedge shaped inner rear walls. the ARA has a large rear firing port and high quality speaker terminals on a solid aluminum binding post plate.</p><p>For a larger speaker with similar design goals look to the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://webdemosbe.xyz/products/rinjani\">RINJANI</a> and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://webdemosbe.xyz/products/rinjani-be\">RINJANI Be</a> which are the larger floor standing siblings of the ARA.</p><p>Please see <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://webdemosbe.xyz/kits/open-source-kits\">Open Source Kits</a> for TeXtreme editions.</p>', 'ara-be', 'admin', 0, '', 1, '', '8', '2-way Bookshelf Speaker Kit', 1, '/uploads/productimage/Ara Be.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/Ara Be-drawing.jpg', '', ''),
('1eb80d60-5f1e-4faf-9854-19c841dbcb26', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '6\" SB16PFCR25-4 / Paper', 0, 0, 'ed8a91c0-2efb-4f49-892e-5f5cb123bd86', '2024-05-06 02:29:13.821', '2026-03-02 06:20:36.421', '<ul><li><p>Vented reinforced plastic chassis</p></li><li><p>Proprietary cone material with natural fibers made in-house</p></li><li><p>Soft low damping rubber surround for improved transient response</p></li><li><p>Optimized motor system</p></li><li><p>Vented coil former for low compression</p></li><li><p>Non-resonant long life lead wires</p></li></ul>', 'sb16pfcr25-4', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/6 inch SB16PFCR25-4-1.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/6 inch SB16PFCR25-4-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/6 inch SB16PFCR25-4-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('1f4dcb0e-1e65-4fcc-bc93-3d48e4dcd5e1', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', 'SATORI 16 MAGNETIC GRILLE', 0, 0, '28c45742-6d1f-44bd-915b-f940e30caf92', '2024-05-08 03:21:09.693', '2026-02-10 08:25:01.073', '<p></p>', '16-magnetic-grille', 'admin', 0, '', 1, '', '3', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/SATORI 16 magnetic grille.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/SATORI 16 Magnetic Grille-drawing.jpg', '', ''),
('20449ecf-5594-4a83-8a4b-5e4197d787e3', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', 'Eka', 0, 0, '28c45742-6d1f-44bd-915b-f940e30caf92', '2024-05-08 03:14:02.285', '2025-10-15 07:03:00.531', '<p>The first commercial kit developed by SB Acoustics. Eka means ‘First son’ the firstborn always emanates special emotions and we feel the same way about Eka. It is a 2-way wooden veneer, or painted speaker with a paper cone 6″ mid-woofer and a 26mm soft dome. This combination works exceptionally well and you get a surprisingly high performance/price ratio. The woofer is a paper pulp cone made in house. You could claim paper is not the newest invention in cone material, true, but optimized correctly paper is an incredibly effective material and as we make it, we control the quality. The low-end performance of this small speaker is very impressive; a deep, controlled and firm system. The 26-mm dome – SB26STAC keeps on impressing when used in real high-end solutions. Smooth, airy and low distortion are just some of the words used to describe this dome and the treble performance of Eka.</p><p><strong>The cabinet:</strong></p><p>High quality 18mm MDF with internal bracing to minimize vibrations. Finish: Walnut, Ebony and black paint, all with deep High-Gloss finish.</p><p><strong>Drivers:</strong></p><ul><li><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://webdemosbe.xyz/products/sb26stac-c000-4\">SB26STAC-C000-4</a></p></li><li><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://webdemosbe.xyz/products/sb17nrxc35-4\">6″ SB17NRXC35-4</a></p></li></ul>', 'eka', 'admin', 0, '', 1, '', '5', '', 0, '/uploads/productimage/Eka-Ebony-HG-e1624671463981-1753057467677.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/SBA-Eka-drawing-scaled-1753057467737.jpg', '', ''),
('21210ff1-6747-4085-9d75-972e6ef7772e', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '10\" SB29NRX75-6 / Norex', 0, 0, '7f514f65-c75e-482d-bf43-66c4f8c08edc', '2024-05-03 07:29:49.584', '2025-12-15 09:48:15.300', '<ul><li><p>Hard paper cone for improved piston operation (made in-house)</p></li><li><p>Vented pole piece for minimum compression</p></li><li><p>Vented cast aluminum chassis for optimum strength and low compression</p></li><li><p>3″ copper voice coil for improved power handling</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li><li><p>Low damping rubber surround for improved dynamic linearity</p></li><li><p>Non-conducting fiber glass voice coil former for minimum damping</p></li></ul>', 'sb29nrx75-6', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/10 inch SB29NRX75-6-1.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/10 inch SB29NRX75-6-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/10 inch SB29NRX75-6-frequency response.jpg', ''),
