('ee53aa81-9feb-4252-9b7f-0adf4a145e0b', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '4\" SB12CACS25-4 / Ceramic', 0, 0, 'ee5d459a-eaec-4159-9082-bdbe673a1ea4', '2024-05-07 01:52:11.586', '2025-12-18 09:56:38.258', '<ul><li><p>Vented cast aluminum chassis for optimum strength and low compression</p></li><li><p>Ceramic cone</p></li><li><p>Soft low damping rubber surround for improved transient response</p></li><li><p>Shorting ring in motor system for reduced distortion</p></li><li><p>Non-conducting fibre glass voice coil former for minimum damping</p></li><li><p>CCAW voice coil for reduced moving mass</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li><li><p>Vented pole piece for reduced compression</p></li></ul>', 'sb12cacs25-4', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/4 inch SB12CACS25-4-1.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/4 inch SB12CACS25-4-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/4 inch SB12CACS25-4-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('eeaee45f-84fc-460f-8374-04a6c1e0bbc6', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', 'SB21RDC-C000-4 / Fabric', 0, 0, '28c45742-6d1f-44bd-915b-f940e30caf92', '2024-05-08 06:33:01.588', '2026-05-18 02:34:30.805', '<ul><li><p>Non-resonant diaphragm design for minimum high frequency break-up</p></li><li><p>Dual balanced compression chamber for improved dynamics</p></li><li><p>Copper cap for reduced voice coil inductance and minimum phase shift</p></li><li><p>Saturation controlled motor system for low distortion</p></li><li><p>Non-reflective rear chamber with optimized damping for improved dynamics</p></li><li><p>Flow optimized vented pole piece for optimum coupling to rear chamber</p></li><li><p>CCAW voice coil for low moving mass</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li><li><p>Low resonance frequency</p></li></ul>', 'sb21rdc-c000-4', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/SB21RDC-C000-4-1.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/SB21RDC-C000-4-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/SB21RDC-C000-4-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('f00282b2-9f16-4f6a-950d-7830ee473803', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '15\" SB42FHCL75-6 / Honeycomb', 0, 0, 'bde0763b-2624-4b11-9f5c-993cd19f68ce', '2024-05-06 05:26:03.237', '2026-03-02 06:26:02.030', '<ul><li><p>Light weight rigid honeycomb cone (hard paper honeycomb with fiber glass skin layers)</p></li><li><p>3″ copper voice coil for improved power handling</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li><li><p>Vented pole piece for minimum compression</p></li><li><p>Vented cast aluminum chassis for optimum strength and low compression</p></li><li><p>Low damping rubber surround for improved dynamic linearity</p></li><li><p>Non-conducting fiber glass voice coil former for minimum damping</p></li><li><p>Large motor system</p></li></ul>', 'sb42fhcl75-6', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/15 inch SB42FHCL75-6.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/15 inch SB42FHCL75-6-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/15 inch SB42FHCL75-6-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('f0efc247-9744-443d-a21d-d856c9e07b21', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '5\" SB15BAC30-8-COAX/ aluminum', 1, 0, '5f43323d-d9ed-4688-8e2f-ff5247083128', '2026-04-01 07:06:32.243', '2026-05-22 09:11:41.081', '<ul><li><p>Geometrically reinforced aluminum cone for optimum piston operation and reduced break-up</p></li><li><p>Low profile rubber surround for minimum high frequency diffraction</p></li><li><p>Soft dome tweeter with neodymium motor and center cavity</p></li><li><p>Excellent high frequency directivity control</p></li><li><p>Extended copper sleeve on pole piece for low inductance and low distortion</p></li><li><p>Light weight CCAW voice coil on fiberglass former</p></li><li><p>Vented cast aluminum chassis</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li></ul>', 'sb15bac30-8-coax', 'admin', 1, 'for more information, click the button below:', 0, '', '', '', 0, '/uploads/productimage/5 inch SB15BAC30-8-COAX.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/5-inch-SB15BAC30-8-COAX-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/5-inch-SB15BAC30-8-COAX-frequency-response.jpg', '/uploads/featuredimages/SB15BAC30-8-COAX-home cover.webp'),
('f1641525-ba68-471d-a91b-4809ec37633b', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '2½\" MD60N-6 / Fabric Dome Filler Driver', 0, 0, '4f3df0be-01fa-438e-9c29-2afc3464a1fc', '2024-04-23 07:10:55.110', '2026-01-06 09:37:47.474', '<ul><li><p>Coated non-resonant soft dome</p></li><li><p>Powerful neodymium motor system</p></li><li><p>Tuned closed-end transmission line chamber</p></li><li><p>Dynamic dome stabilizer and flow resistor</p></li><li><p>Machined aluminium faceplate</p></li><li><p>Vented coil former</p></li><li><p>Braided long-life silver litz wires</p></li></ul>', 'md60n-6', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/2.5 inch SATORI MD60N-6.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/2.5 inch SATORI MD60N-6-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/2.5 inch SATORI MD60N-6-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('f1bf569a-8fe8-476d-bb03-aa12173a4d8c', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', 'Arya', 0, 0, '28c45742-6d1f-44bd-915b-f940e30caf92', '2024-05-08 02:53:33.396', '2026-04-30 02:09:54.231', '<p>The ARYA is a floor standing 2½-way speaker kit. Arya means “wise man” and we believe Arya is the wise choice if you want an elegant hih performance floor standing speaker.</p><p>Each speaker uses tow <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://webdemosbe.xyz/products/sb17mfc35-8\">6″ SB17MFC</a> mineral filled poly cone woofers for a tight satisfying bass and clean crisp mids. The SB Acoustics mineral filled poly cones are of a special composition and we are confident poly cones have never sounded better.</p><p>With 2 x 6″ woofers per side there is enough quality bass for room sizes of 50m2/500f2 or more. The tweeter is the very renowned and patented <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://webdemosbe.xyz/products/sb29rdac-c000-4\">Ring Dome</a>. the large 29mm dome with centre termination and wide ultra linear suspension results in a very low distortion and a presentation that can be described as very “silent/black” background.</p>', 'arya', 'admin', 0, '', 1, '', '10', '2½-way Floor Standing Speaker Kit', 1, '/uploads/productimage/Arya.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/Arya-drawing.jpg', '', ''),
('f3abcae2-c6e4-4942-9fd6-8eeda3746076', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '7½\" MW19PF-8 / Paper', 0, 0, '684c7a61-8852-4ac8-81b0-b059c3aa3ece', '2024-05-03 05:24:03.426', '2026-01-07 10:04:39.925', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 0, 19);\"><strong>To be discontinued from standard product range, available to OEM minimum order quantity 250 pcs.</strong></span></p><ul><li><p>Vented aerodynamic cast aluminium chassis for optimum strength and low compression.</p></li><li><p>Proprietary cone material with EGYPTIAN PAPYRUS™ fibres made in-house.</p></li><li><p>Soft low damping rubber surround for optimum transient response.</p></li><li><p>Advanced BIMAX spider for improved linearity.</p></li><li><p>Non-conducting fibre glass voice coil former for minimum damping.</p></li><li><p>Extended copper sleeve on pole piece for low inductance and reduced distortion.</p></li><li><p>CCAW voice coil for reduced moving mass.</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires attached 180° apart for improved stability.</p></li><li><p>Vented pole piece and coil former for reduced compression.</p></li><li><p>Low piston to chassis diameter ratio.</p></li><li><p>Gasket and bolt hole protrusions for reduced coupling to speaker cabinet.</p></li></ul>', 'mw19pf-8', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/7.5 inch SATORI MW19PF-8-1.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/7.5 inch SATORI MW19PF-8-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/7.5 inch SATORI MW19PF-8-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('f3ca7aca-373e-4766-8cd4-298fcb123b71', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '10\" SW26DBAC76-3-DV / Aluminum', 0, 0, '7f514f65-c75e-482d-bf43-66c4f8c08edc', '2024-05-06 03:57:50.662', '2026-05-18 02:45:16.504', '<ul><li><p>Unique patented long throw shallow design</p></li><li><p>Vented cast aluminum chassis for optimum strength and low compression</p></li><li><p>Dual rigid aluminum cone structure</p></li><li><p>Non-conducting fiber glass coil former for minimum damping</p></li><li><p>Shorting ring in motor system for reduced distortion</p></li><li><p>Copper voice coil for improved power handling</p></li><li><p>Dual voice coil</p></li><li><p>Long life insulated silver lead wires</p></li><li><p>Powerful neodymium motor system</p></li></ul>', 'sw26dbac76-3-dv', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/10 inch SW26DBAC76-3-DV.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/10 inch SW26DBAC76-3-DV-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/10 inch SW26DBAC76-3-DV-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('f42bb052-58aa-419d-bb0e-e84c9c67a010', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '8\" SB23CACS45-8 / Ceramic', 0, 0, '3ceafaeb-f3e4-4034-b46a-44948d3c2062', '2024-05-07 01:48:55.410', '2026-05-29 07:11:12.768', '<ul><li><p>Soft low damping rubber surround for improved ransient response</p></li><li><p>Geometrically reinforced ceramic cone for improved break-up control</p></li><li><p>Shorting ring in motor system for reduced distortion</p></li><li><p>Vented pole piece for reduced compression</p></li><li><p>Vented cast aluminium chassis for optimum strength and low compression</p></li><li><p>Shallow design</p></li><li><p>Non-conducting fibre glass voice coil former for minimum damping</p></li><li><p>CCAW voice coil for reduced moving mass</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li></ul>', 'sb23cacs45-8', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/8 inch SB23CACS25-8-1.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/8 inch SB23CACS45-8-drawing-1.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/8 inch SB23CACS45-8-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('f5479ee0-54e0-47d8-9444-11f303820001', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', 'Tifa 8', 0, 0, '28c45742-6d1f-44bd-915b-f940e30caf92', '2025-05-23 07:21:36.097', '2026-04-28 01:16:27.689', '<p><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Open Source Kit: Not available as full kit, read below for details.<br></strong></span></p><p>Tifa 8 is an impressive 3 way floor-standing speaker staying true to the unique Danish design language of the Tifa family. The Tifa 8 features a dedicated 6-inch natural fiber cone midrange housed in it’s own sealed midrange chamber. The highest octaves are handed off to the 26mm fine weave fabric soft dome known for it’s undistorted smooth and dynamic sound.</p><p>Dual 8-inch woofer anchor the lower frequencies with deep, tight bass. The Tifa inclined cabinet design optimizes driver time alignment, offering precise imaging. Crafted with precision, the robust MDF construction and strategic bracing minimize vibrations, providing a pure, uncolored listening experience.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><em>Open Source Kit</em></strong></p><p><em>Tifa 8 is an open source kit meaning the speaker is fully developed and documented by SB Acoustics and you are free to use the plans.</em></p>', 'tifa-8', 'admin', 0, '', 1, '', '3', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/Tifa 8-1752473445742.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/Tifa 8-drawing.jpg', '', ''),
('f5dc60cf-2e2f-4206-8272-b082105fcc54', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '10\" SB26SFCL38-8 / Paper', 0, 0, '7f514f65-c75e-482d-bf43-66c4f8c08edc', '2024-04-18 07:06:08.032', '2025-12-16 08:27:37.224', '<ul><li><p>Hard pressed vented paper cone</p></li><li><p>Durable rubber surround</p></li><li><p>Symmetric suspension</p></li><li><p>Non-conductive coil former</p></li><li><p>Long life litz wires</p></li><li><p>Vented chassis</p></li><li><p>Bucking magnet</p></li></ul>', 'sb26sfcl38-8', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/10 inch SB26SFCL38-8-1.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/10 inch SB26SFCL38-8-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/10 inch SB26SFCL38-8-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('f73eb673-d9a8-4c15-a2e1-c07582d5f37c', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', 'TW29DN-8 / Fabric', 0, 0, '28c45742-6d1f-44bd-915b-f940e30caf92', '2024-05-08 04:11:17.736', '2026-05-28 07:00:41.106', '<ul><li><p>Large surround dome for increased acoustic output</p></li><li><p>Dual balanced compression chamber for improved dynamics</p></li><li><p>Dual copper caps for absolute minimum voice coil inductance and minimum phase shift</p></li><li><p>Two part aluminium faceplate with integrated mechanical decoupling</p></li><li><p>High saturation neodymium motor system with T-shaped pole piece for lower distortion</p></li><li><p>Non-reflective cast aluminium chamber with optimized damping for improved dynamics</p></li><li><p>Shallow flow magnet structure for optimum coupling to rear chamber</p></li><li><p>CCAW voice coil for low moving mass</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li><li><p>Low resonance frequency for extended range</p></li></ul>', 'tw29dn-8', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/SATORI TW29DN-8-1.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/SATORI TW29DN-8-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/SATORI TW29DN-8-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('f832185a-0e79-4dbe-bffb-6fc0aaaf1bf3', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '6\" SB17NRX2L35-8 / Norex', 0, 0, 'ed8a91c0-2efb-4f49-892e-5f5cb123bd86', '2025-05-23 07:08:40.945', '2026-05-18 02:38:27.007', '<ul><li><p>Vented cast aluminum chassis for optimum strength and low compression</p></li><li><p>Proprietary cone material with natural fibers made in-house</p></li><li><p>Soft low damping rubber surround for transient response</p></li><li><p>Non-conducting fiber glass voice coil former for minimum damping</p></li><li><p>Extra large motor with extended copper sleeve on pole piece</p></li><li><p>Vented coil former</p></li><li><p>CCAW voice coil for reduced moving mass</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li><li><p>Vented pole piece for reduced compression</p></li></ul>', 'sb17nrx2l35-8', 'admin', 1, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/6 inch SB17NRX2L35-8-1.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/6 inch SB17NRX2L35-8-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/6 inch SB17NRX2L35-8-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('f90dd744-317e-4a6f-b4c5-d7c02270c198', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', 'Tifa 6', 0, 0, '28c45742-6d1f-44bd-915b-f940e30caf92', '2025-05-23 07:34:46.435', '2026-05-29 07:26:01.457', '<p><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Open Source Kit: Not available as full kit, read below for details.<br></strong></span></p><p>The playful design of the Tifa 6 follows in the footsteps of the renowned Danish engineered SB Acoustics speakers. The sound is open and transparent, free from unwanted standing waves and reflection thanks to the elegantly slanted cabinet.</p><p>The Tifa 6 is true HiFi in a small package and fits perfectly in any living room. The sound presents as very natural, articulate and refined yet with a warm character with satisfying bass thanks to the natural fiber cone 6-inch midwoofer paired with our 26mm fine weave soft fabric dome tweeter.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><em>Open Source Kit</em></strong></p><p><em>Tifa 6 is an open source kit meaning the speaker is fully developed and documented by SB Acoustics and you are free to use the plans.</em></p>', 'tifa-6', 'admin', 0, '', 1, '', '2', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/Tifa 6-1752473417061.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/Tifa 6-drawing.jpg', '', ''),
('fa06264e-00d5-4adf-95b8-51258f40b6c1', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '4\" SB12PFCR25-4-COAX', 0, 0, 'ee5d459a-eaec-4159-9082-bdbe673a1ea4', '2024-04-23 07:26:38.443', '2025-12-10 06:53:07.440', '<ul><li><p>Vented reinforced plastic chassis</p></li><li><p>Proprietary cone material with natural fibers made in-house</p></li><li><p>Soft low damping rubber surround for improved transient response</p></li><li><p>Optimized motor system</p></li><li><p>Non-resonant long life lead wires</p></li><li><p>Compact large surround dome tweeter</p></li></ul>', 'sb12pfcr25-4-coax', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/4 inch SB12PFCR25-4-COAX.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/4 inch SB12PFCR25-4-COAX-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/4 inch SB12PFCR25-4-COAX-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('fad498db-9a64-4e66-a25c-f7d7a30c1ad7', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '5x8\" SB15SFCR39-8 / Paper', 0, 0, '3ceafaeb-f3e4-4034-b46a-44948d3c2062', '2024-05-06 03:33:49.230', '2025-12-30 10:03:54.738', '<ul><li><p>Racetrack design</p></li><li><p>Hard paper cone (made in-house)</p></li><li><p>Optimized motor system</p></li><li><p>Non-conductive reinforced vented coil former</p></li><li><p>Symmetric suspension</p></li><li><p>Low damping rubber surround</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li><li><p>Vented chassis</p></li></ul>', 'sb15sfcr39-8', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/5x8 inch SB15SFCR39-8.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/5x8 inch SB15SFCR39-8-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/5x8 inch SB15SFCR39-8-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('fb3a9caf-1902-440a-ae72-0bce9fb52549', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '5\" MR13PNW-4 / Paper', 0, 0, '5f43323d-d9ed-4688-8e2f-ff5247083128', '2024-05-07 02:18:50.946', '2026-01-06 03:32:58.228', '<ul><li><p>Vented aerodynamic cast aluminium chassis for optimum strength and low compression</p></li><li><p>Proprietary cone material with EGYPTIAN PAPYRUS fibres made in-house</p></li><li><p>Soft low damping rubber surround for optimum transient response</p></li><li><p>Advanced BIMAX spider for improved linearity</p></li><li><p>Powerful optimized low distortion neodymium motor system</p></li><li><p>Non-conducting fibre glass voice coil former for minimum damping</p></li><li><p>Extended copper sleeve on pole piece for low inductance and reduced distortion</p></li><li><p>CCAW voice coil for reduced moving mass</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires attached 180° apart for improved stability</p></li><li><p>Vented pole piece and coil former for reduced compression</p></li><li><p>Low piston to chassis diameter ratio</p></li><li><p>Gasket and bolt hole protrusions for reduced coupling to speaker cabinet</p></li></ul>', 'mr13pnw-4', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/5 inch SATORI MR13PNW-4-1.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/5 inch SATORI MR13PNW-4-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/5 inch SATORI MR13PNW-4-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('fbc9d4d9-ebd0-48eb-9109-adacec484983', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '7½\" MT19CP-8 / paper', 0, 0, '684c7a61-8852-4ac8-81b0-b059c3aa3ece', '2024-05-03 03:26:08.027', '2026-05-22 09:04:53.377', '<ul><li><p>Vented cast aluminium chassis</p></li><li><p>Proprietary cone material with EGYPTIAN PAPYRUS made in house</p></li><li><p>Powerful low distortion neodymium motor system with extended copper sleeve</p></li><li><p>Low profile surround for minimum high frequency diffraction</p></li><li><p>Light weight CCAW voice coil on fibre glass former</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li><li><p>Soft dome tweeter with neodymium motor, copper cap and CCAW voice coil</p></li></ul>', 'mt19cp-8', 'admin', 0, 'for more information, click the button below:', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/7.5 inch SATORI MT19CP-8.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/7.5 inch SATORI MT19CP-8-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/7.5 inch SATORI MT19CP-8-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('fce3bf90-300a-426c-875c-e1ef707c468f', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '7½\" MW19TX-4 / TeXtreme', 0, 0, '684c7a61-8852-4ac8-81b0-b059c3aa3ece', '2024-05-03 06:05:50.048', '2025-12-17 09:17:27.752', '<ul><li><p>Advanced TeXtreme® cone</p></li><li><p>Vented aerodynamic cast aluminium chassis</p></li><li><p>Soft low damping rubber surround</p></li><li><p>Advanced BIMAX spider</p></li><li><p>Powerful optimized low distortion neodymium motor system</p></li><li><p>Extended copper sleeve on pole piece</p></li><li><p>Non-conducting fiberglass voice coil former</p></li><li><p>Vented pole piece and voice coil</p></li><li><p>Light weight CCAW voice coil</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li></ul>', 'mw19tx-4', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/7.5 inch SATORI MW19TX-4.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/7.5 inch SATORI MW19TX-4-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/7.5 inch SATORI MW19TX-4-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('fd337162-e051-4809-aac4-fedcc91ce4c7', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', 'SB26ST-C000-5 / Fabric', 0, 0, '28c45742-6d1f-44bd-915b-f940e30caf92', '2024-05-08 06:50:21.346', '2026-04-06 01:48:03.153', '<ul><li><p>Optimized damping in pole cavity to eliminate internal reflection</p></li><li><p>Fine weave soft fabric dome for smooth frequency response</p></li><li><p>Saturation controlled motor system for reduced distortion</p></li><li><p>CCAW voice coil for low moving mass</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li></ul>', 'sb26st-c000-5', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/SB26ST-C000-5-1.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/SB26ST-C000-5-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/SB26ST-C000-5-frequency response.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `product` (`id`, `brandId`, `name`, `isFeatured`, `isArchived`, `sizeId`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt`, `description`, `slug`, `updatedBy`, `isNewProduct`, `featuredDesc`, `isKits`, `navbarNotes`, `priority`, `searchbox_desc`, `tempAllFinished`, `cover_img_url`, `drawing_img_url`, `graph_img_url`, `featured_img_url`) VALUES
('fdaea94f-46f2-42c1-a85b-c5256ebaa1bf', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', 'SB21RDCN-C000-4 / Fabric', 0, 0, '28c45742-6d1f-44bd-915b-f940e30caf92', '2024-05-03 06:13:55.906', '2026-04-15 01:48:25.356', '<ul><li><p>Non-resonant diaphragm design for minimum high frequency break-up</p></li><li><p>Copper cap for reduced voice coil inductance and minimum phase shift</p></li><li><p>Compact low distortion neodymium motor system</p></li><li><p>Non-resonant rear chamber with optimized damping for improved dynamics</p></li><li><p>CCAW voice coil for low moving mass</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li><li><p>Low resonance frequency</p></li></ul>', 'sb21rdcn-c000-4', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/SB21RDCN-C000-4.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/SB21RDCN-C000-4-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/SB21RDCN-C000-4-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('fdf4ff43-0c27-403c-b333-a1845b0f27bb', '9e2a9f31-bce3-48ff-b438-0a00f8f8ec0b', 'BIANCO-15OB350', 0, 0, '0829acf6-a413-48bd-98a3-de816ea9e77b', '2025-09-17 08:41:25.161', '2026-05-29 08:47:41.448', '<ul><li><p>Proprietary cone paper material made in-house</p></li><li><p>Vented pole piece for reduced compression</p></li><li><p>Minimum damping fiber glass voice coil former</p></li><li><p>2.5\" voice coil</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li><li><p>Weather-proof coated cone paper</p></li><li><p>Designed for open baffle applications</p></li></ul>', 'bianco-15ob350', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 0, '/uploads/productimage/BIANCO-15OB350-1.webp', '/uploads/productdrawing/BIANCO-15OB350-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/BIANCO-15OB350-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('fe4caf0f-7321-431a-a7b2-2d2f88ee8fa6', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '10\" SW26DBAC76-8 / Aluminum', 0, 0, '7f514f65-c75e-482d-bf43-66c4f8c08edc', '2024-05-06 04:01:20.585', '2025-12-11 10:22:17.804', '<ul><li><p>Unique patented long throw shallow design</p></li><li><p>Vented cast aluminum chassis for optimum strength and low compression</p></li><li><p>Dual rigid aluminum cone structure</p></li><li><p>Non-conducting fiber glass coil former for minimum damping</p></li><li><p>Shorting ring in motor system for reduced distortion</p></li><li><p>Copper voice coil for improved power handling</p></li><li><p>Long life insulated silver lead wires</p></li><li><p>Powerful neodymium motor system</p></li></ul>', 'sw26dbac76-8', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/10 inch SW26DBAC76-8.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/10 inch SW26DBAC76-8-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/10 inch SW26DBAC76-8-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('fe78c0e0-469b-424c-9ef2-a34880f322ac', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '4\" SB12MNRX2-25-4 / Norex', 0, 0, 'ee5d459a-eaec-4159-9082-bdbe673a1ea4', '2024-05-06 03:12:04.483', '2026-01-06 02:56:13.590', '<ul><li><p>Proprietary cone material with natural fibres made in-house</p></li><li><p>Shortened voice coil optimized for pure midrange reproduction</p></li><li><p>High damping Butyl rubber surround for non-resonant sound character</p></li><li><p>Vented pole piece for reduced compression</p></li><li><p>Vented cast aluminium chassis for optimum strength and low compression</p></li><li><p>CCAW voice coil for reduced moving mass</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires</p></li><li><p>Non-conducting fibre glass coil former for minimum damping</p></li><li><p>Shorting ring in motor system for reduced distortion</p></li></ul>', 'sb12mnrx2-25-4', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/4 inch SB12MNRX2-25-4.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/4 inch SB12MNRX2-25-4-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/4 inch SB12MNRX2-25-4-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('ff84938f-509f-4173-902e-274da0befd69', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '5\" MR13P-8 / Paper', 0, 0, '5f43323d-d9ed-4688-8e2f-ff5247083128', '2024-05-07 02:56:00.379', '2026-01-06 03:27:33.945', '<ul><li><p>Vented aerodynamic cast aluminium chassis for optimum strength and low compression.</p></li><li><p>Proprietary cone material with EGYPTIAN PAPYRUS™ fibres made in-house.</p></li><li><p>Soft low damping rubber surround for optimum transient response.</p></li><li><p>Advanced BIMAX spider for improved linearity.</p></li><li><p>Powerful optimized low distortion neodymium motor system.</p></li><li><p>Non-conducting fibre glass voice coil former for minimum damping.</p></li><li><p>Extended copper sleeve on pole piece for low inductance and reduced distortion.</p></li><li><p>CCAW voice coil for reduced moving mass.</p></li><li><p>Long life silver lead wires attached 180° apart for improved stability.</p></li><li><p>Vented pole piece and coil former for reduced compression.</p></li><li><p>Low piston to chassis diameter ratio.</p></li><li><p>Gasket and bolt hole protrusions for reduced coupling to speaker cabinet.</p></li></ul>', 'mr13p-8', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1, '/uploads/productimage/5 inch SATORI MR13P-8.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/5 inch SATORI MR13P-8-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/5 inch SATORI MR13P-8-frequency response.jpg', ''),
('ffacf733-e64d-4c02-99b8-2f3bc6714ae3', '680c5eee-7ed7-41bc-b14b-4185f8a1c379', '5\" SB13PFC25-4-COAX / Paper', 0, 0, '5f43323d-d9ed-4688-8e2f-ff5247083128', '2024-05-06 07:12:04.006', '2026-03-02 06:29:47.762', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 0, 19);\"><strong>To be discontinued from standard product range, available to OEM minimum order quantity 200 pcs.</strong></span></p><ul><li><p>Vented reinforced plastic chassis</p></li><li><p>Proprietary cone material with natural fibers made in-house</p></li><li><p>Soft low damping rubber surround for improved transient response</p></li><li><p>Optimized motor system</p></li><li><p>Non-resonant long life lead wires</p></li><li><p>Compact large surround dome tweeter</p></li></ul>', 'sb13pfc25-4-coax', 'admin', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 0, '/uploads/productimage/5 inch SB13PFC25-4-COAX.jpg', '/uploads/productdrawing/5 inch SB13PFC25-4-COAX-drawing.jpg', '/uploads/productfrequencyresponse/5 inch SB13PFC25-4-COAX-frequency response.jpg', '');
